videos.headline: Bueckers to Edwards for the and-1 bucket
videos.description: Huskies get some swift ball movement from Paige Bueckers to Aaliyah Edwards who knocks down the layup while drawing the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Bueckers to Edwards for the and-1 bucket) 2021/03/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bueckers with the steal and the bucket
videos.description: Paige Bueckers making moves on both ends of the floor, as she intercepts the pass and knocks down the layup on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Bueckers with the steal and the bucket) 2021/03/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bueckers, Griffin making quick buckets for the Huskies
videos.description: Paige Bueckers quickly answers a Syracuse bucket with a jumper, then seconds later Aubrey Griffin steals and scores adding more UConn points.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (Bueckers, Griffin making quick buckets for the Huskies) 2021/03/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nelson-Ododa and Williams connect down low
videos.description: Olivia Nelson-Ododa patiently waits then dishes the bounce pass to Christyn Williams for the bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Nelson-Ododa and Williams connect down low) 2021/03/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bueckers' no-look pass sets up Nelson-Ododa for 2
videos.description: Paige Bueckers gets the skillful pass through traffic to Olivia Nelson-Ododa who scores the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Bueckers' no-look pass sets up Nelson-Ododa for 2) 2021/03/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bueckers leads UConn past Syracuse and to the Sweet 16
videos.description: Paige Bueckers scores 20 points as UConn knocks Syracuse out the NCAA tournament and moves on to the Sweet 16.
